== How to install

You can install Rabbit by RubyGems or package system on your platform.

=== Hot to install by RubyGems

  % gem install rabbit

=== How to install on Debian GNU/Linux

  % sudo aptitude install -y rabbit

=== How to install on Ubuntu

  % sudo aptitude install -y rabbit

